      World news story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Call for bids: supporting inclusive politics in Iraq
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The British Embassy in Baghdad, Iraq is accepting proposals for a 2-3 year project starting in early 2021 under its Conflict, Stability and Security Fund.</p>

  </div>
</div>

